des:
This skill is strictly created for free users of the popular Alexa skill Dinosaur Sounds, and who don't intend to upgrade...

Dinosaur Sounds, listen to the most amazing sounds of these extinct species.

The dinosaur sounds available are;

Tee Rex (Tyrannosaurus Rex)
Acrocanthosaurus
Giganotosaurus
Dilophosaurus
Allosaurus
Spinosaurus
Brachiosaurus
Stegosaurus
Raptor (Velociraptor)
Triceratops

***TWO NEW SOUNDS ADDED***
Brontosaurus
Troodon

To listen to any of the dinosaur sounds, just mention the names above correctly.

Reawaken the extinct dinosaur sounds in your living room.
